<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١٧٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذَرَأنَا}</span> ... خَلَقْنَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُلْحِدُونَ}</span> ... يَمِيلُونَ عَنِ الْحَقِّ فِي أَسْمَائِهِ؛ كَأَنْ يُسَمُّوا آلِهَتَهُمْ بِأَسْمَائِهِ، أَوْ فِي مَعَانِيهَا بِتَحْرِيفِهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٨١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَعْدِلُونَ}</span> ... يَقْضُونَ، وَيَحْكُمُونَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَنَسْتَدْرِجُهُم}</span> ... سِنَفْتَحُ لَهُمُ الأَرْزَاقَ؛ لِيَغْتَرُّوا، ثُمَّ نُبَاغِتُهُمْ بِالْعُقُوبَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأُمْلِي لَهُمْ}</span> ... أَمْهِلُهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَتِينٌ}</span> ... قَوِيٌّ، شَدِيدٌ، لَا يُدْفَعُ بِقُوَّةٍ، وَلَا حِيلَةٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جِنَّةٍ}</span> ... جُنُونٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَعْمَهُونَ}</span> ... يَتَحَيَّرُونَ، وَيَتَرَدَّدُونَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَيَّانَ مُرْسَاهَا}</span> ... مَتَى وُقُوعُهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُجَلِّيهَا}</span> ... يُظْهِرُهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ثَقُلَتْ}</span> ... عَظُمَ عِلْمُهَا، وَخَفِيَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٨٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَفِيٌّ عَنْهَا}</span> ... حَرِيصٌ عَلَى الْعِلْمِ بِهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
